about_us: Trans express logistics is an international logistics company headquartered in Namangan, Uzbekistan. Despite the fact that the company started its activity only 5 years ago, it managed to have its loyal customers in more than 20 countries. Currently, we provide prompt and high quality services to all European and Asian countries regardless of the circumstances. All your requirements are our goal. Let us now take care of your shipment reaching its owner.¬† Your trust is our greatest weapon. In order to earn that trust, we maintain regular communication with our highly skilled drivers and consultants, ensuring that we can offer you the most competitive and cost-effective pricing.
reliability_desc: We guarantee that your product/merchandise will reach its destination at the specified time. All our trucks have passed quality control tests.
affordable_price_desc: Attention! Our most convenient and serviceable prices are for you. If you become our permanent customer using our continuous services, even more convenient prices await you. Go far, faster and cheaper with us!
expert_support_desc: Get the attention you want from us. We can be your friend and partner. We offer you the services of our best experts with an individual approach.
transportation_management_desc: Due to our strategic approach, we take full control of the transportation process from destination to destination. Without any intervention from you, your cargo will reach its destination without any defects.
responsible_drivers_desc: Each of our drivers is experienced and responsible. We conduct our own tests before sending each of them and find the best one for you. All our drivers are experienced and experts in their field.
